body.description: Introducing the perfect workspace solution for those who appreciate coastal and farmhouse styling - the Key West 60W Reversible L Shaped Desk. This L shape office desk provides ample space and durability to spread out your computer, books, paperwork, and more, making it perfect for working on your next project or assignment. Its sturdy post leg design and unique X pattern accents on the side panels create a relaxed, open appearance that gives the L-shaped computer desk an easy-going charm. This reversible L shaped table is designed to fit seamlessly in your home office, and its spacious corner desk surface allows you to work comfortably and efficiently. With several attractive finish options available, you can easily find the perfect look for your space. The L Desk is constructed from high-quality materials that ensure it can handle any task you throw at it. With a weight capacity of up to 200 pounds, this writing desk can support all your work essentials and more. Upgrade your home office with a variety of coordinating Key West products, including office chairs, file cabinets, accent cabinets, bookcases, and more (sold separately). This L computer desk is perfect for any professional setting and will add a touch of elegance to your work environment. It is also an excellent choice for students and gamers alike, providing ample space to work, study, or play. Based in Jamestown, N.Y., Bush Furniture has been a trusted manufacturer of ready-to-assemble furniture for over 60 years. We pride ourselves on being your one-stop-shop for high-quality home furnishings at an exceptional value. Our growing collection of unique designs allows you to outfit your living space with safe, stylish solutions that fit every room and any budget. If you are looking for a work desk that is both functional and stylish, the Key West 60W Reversible L Shaped Desk is an excellent choice.

Safe and Stylish Residential Furniture With an array of products across several categories, Bush Furniture gives you the opportunity to outfit your entire home with appealing and reliable furniture. Sustainable Materials Not only do engineered wood products begin life as a recycled product, but more than 95% of a tree can be used for the production of particleboard, versus 63% for solid lumber. A Proud Legacy Based in Jamestown, N.Y., Bush Furniture has been a leading manufacturer of ready-to-assemble furniture for over 60 years.

Is this product made from solid wood? Key West products are not solid wood. They are manufactured using engineered wood with a laminate finish. Is assembly required? Key West products do not arrive pre-assembled, but most items are designed for installation in 60 minutes or less. What if I'm missing parts/instructions? We aim to include all necessary materials with our products. If an item has been left out by mistake, our U.S.-based customer support team can help issue a replacement.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Well designed and practical desk.
reviews.reviewText: This desk went together easily and quickly. My mom and dad helped me, so it is easy for 3 adults to put together. It is sturdy and beautiful and holds 2 computer work stations perfectly. I am very pleased with it! The cottage style makes me happy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars What a great desk!
reviews.reviewText: This desk is great! it looks way more expensive than it is, very sturdy and the instructions and all pieces are clearly marked, making putting it together a breeze! it says you need two ppl to put it together, but I had no problems doing it by myself. It does take a while as there are lots of steps/screws/bolts/kams, but its super easy and everything is clearly marked. The finish is a beautiful gray [as pictured] and the size is perfect for the room space. I am very pleased. Buy this desk --- you won't be disappointed!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful and sturdy
reviews.reviewText: Wood finish is beautiful. Looks great and was easy to put together. Packaging was excellent. Very pleased with this product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Great desk and sturdy and a good price. The other furniture pieces however are not the same quality.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is a very sturdy and well built desk. Also one of the easiest things I have ever assembled. Instructions were clear and simple. Really looks great. Highly recommend. The box weighed a ton.. you will need two people to carry it into your house.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great corner desk
reviews.reviewText: Furniture that requires assembly always makes me unsure until its completely assembled. I assembled this desk in an hour and I cant rave about it more. It came with detailed instructions and the hardware had part numbers that were listed at each step in the instructions so I knew which set to use.This desk is sturdy, looks great and fits perfectly in my office. Love this purchase, I highly recommend.
